    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Restaurants, usually located below street level, patterned after basements or cellars in German city halls where wine and beer are sold.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
